      <odd id="aspace_82eca6a827f0501065b32d1ffd1909f6">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 5-B (YRG 5-B), Accounting records and records of the Yale comptroller.</p>  
      </odd>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_dfd64496a6f14216a89fe3047b4c80ee">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>Access to the records is restricted to the office of origin only.</p>
         <p>Some records in this finding aid have been redacted, as they include student names, donor names, and other restricted data. These records will not appear in the published finding aid.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_025cba1ca2303ce42452327b1d1bb42c">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Assistant Comptroller for Estates, Trusts and Taxes, Yale University, Records (RU 544). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_755dc683e0505f399f2881a0af73936b">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of reports, subject files, agreements, tax and audit files, financial statements, and memoranda documenting the operations of the assistant comptroller for estates, trusts and taxes at Yale.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_7aa577661287d9bf08cd359e36af6e15">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The collection is arranged by accession.</p>  
      </arrangement>
